last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 3
last_episode_to_air.overview: Dan Snow eyes something suspicious about Tut's burial items. Raksha Dave gets a look into the mummification process and new 3D scanning tech being used. And John Sergeant explores some ancient footwork.

name: Tutankhamun with Dan Snow
overview: An investigative look into the life of the boy-king, his environment and his death.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Dan Snow, and the team go to Egypt for a look at what might have been Tut's life around the time of his death. They'll visit the new Egyptian History Museum, visit important unearthed ancient communities and sample food, and beer from the period.
